title: Taran Killam on Star Wars
itunes:title: Taran Killam on Star Wars
description:
You may know Taran Killam from his six season run on Saturday Night Live. But he's been a busy dude since then, acting, writing and directing on screen and stage. Chuck had the pleasure of sitting down and talking about his movie crush, a little film called STAR WARS.
